Class ChainedDataStructure<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • structures.commons.ChainedDataStructure<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Generic type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, DataStructure<T>, LinearDataStructure<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinkedList, Queue, Stack

    public abstract class ChainedDataStructure<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements LinearDataStructure<T>
    Abstract class to be implemented by all types of LinkedLists, and data structures that are dynamically size, but we do not know how many elements we will start with / have.
